<i>Katei no Jijo / A Family Matter (1962)</i>

3
00:01:24,580 --> 00:01:26,318
I wish I had 500,000 yen

4
00:01:27,003 --> 00:01:29,723
I have 50,000 yen in my bank account.

5
00:01:30,830 --> 00:01:36,014
50,000 yen... that's 1/10.

6
00:01:36,438 --> 00:01:37,598
Do you have it?

7
00:01:37,976 --> 00:01:38,456
No.

8
00:01:38,590 --> 00:01:39,264
Not at all?

9
00:01:39,595 --> 00:01:41,708
Just little bit, 10,000 yen? But if this is the case,

10
00:01:41,945 --> 00:01:43,105
Just 10000yen?

11
00:01:43,550 --> 00:01:46,434
we might not be able to get married for a while

12
00:01:46,459 --> 00:01:47,856
For the time being?

13
00:01:48,540 --> 00:01:49,761
Maybe a year from now?

14
00:01:50,290 --> 00:01:51,337
It may be two years

15
00:01:52,403 --> 00:01:54,161
or maybe never

16
00:01:54,186 --> 00:01:55,474
I don't like that.

17
00:01:56,337 --> 00:01:58,603
I've been saying that for a while.

18
00:01:59,266 --> 00:02:02,945
My older brother who paid for my college education like a parent

19
00:02:03,002 --> 00:02:04,792
Now he's  trying to issue a dishonored bill.

20
00:02:04,817 --> 00:02:05,862
Is the problem different?

21
00:02:05,886 --> 00:02:07,031
It's the same

22
00:02:07,056 --> 00:02:09,636
My brother's family is in such a difficult situation

23
00:02:09,780 --> 00:02:12,060
I'm not going to get married with a cool face

24
00:02:12,060 --> 00:02:13,051
Can I say that?

25
00:02:14,080 --> 00:02:16,327
Please use my 50000yen for him.

26
00:02:16,710 --> 00:02:18,345
Thank you.

27
00:02:18,685 --> 00:02:20,545
But He needs 500,000 yen

28
00:02:20,570 --> 00:02:21,857
It'll help a little, right?

29
00:02:21,881 --> 00:02:23,750
It's like a drop in the bucket .

30
00:02:23,750 --> 00:02:26,860
And I don't want to cause you any trouble

31
00:02:26,860 --> 00:02:27,686
Don't worry.

32
00:02:27,710 --> 00:02:33,760
Ah, I've come to your neighborhood. Let's say goodbye

33
00:02:33,760 --> 00:02:35,846
I'll bring it to you tomorrow

34
00:02:36,362 --> 00:02:37,562
I feel sorry.

35
00:02:38,227 --> 00:02:40,236
You don't like me?

36
00:02:40,310 --> 00:02:40,983
No way.

37
00:02:41,127 --> 00:02:41,829
Really?

38
00:02:41,854 --> 00:02:42,370
Really.

39
00:03:09,242 --> 00:03:10,843
Fumi is late.

40
00:03:10,957 --> 00:03:15,025
Oh, maybe she is working overtime?

41
00:03:15,050 --> 00:03:16,830
or maybe she is at bar with a guy now.

42
00:03:16,830 --> 00:03:18,537
You shouldn't talk it carelessly.

43
00:03:18,561 --> 00:03:19,880
It's not lie.

44
00:03:19,880 --> 00:03:21,130
I saw the scene properly.

45
00:03:21,130 --> 00:03:21,614
What's he like?

46
00:03:21,638 --> 00:03:24,000
Well, I guess I could say he's handsome

47
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:25,260
But he's not really to my taste

48
00:03:25,847 --> 00:03:27,193
What's he like?

49
00:03:27,531 --> 00:03:29,304
What should I say?

50
00:03:29,604 --> 00:03:30,840
You know,like Ginnan.

51
00:03:30,840 --> 00:03:31,350
Ginshio?

52
00:03:31,502 --> 00:03:32,817
No...

53
00:03:32,842 --> 00:03:33,478
Gin-nagashi?

54
00:03:33,515 --> 00:03:34,533
Yes,that's it.

55
00:03:34,558 --> 00:03:35,127
What's that?

56
00:03:35,227 --> 00:03:37,280
You know the old words.

57
00:03:38,132 --> 00:03:41,868
It was nice bath.
I washed all my body.

58
00:03:43,690 --> 00:03:46,350
Oh...

59
00:03:46,630 --> 00:03:49,170
I was charged 500 yen.

60
00:03:49,510 --> 00:03:51,645
This wine is the finest from France,

61
00:03:52,172 --> 00:03:55,070
so I'll have to split the cost

62
00:03:55,070 --> 00:03:55,752
Yes..

63
00:03:56,210 --> 00:03:57,510
You don't have to pay.

64
00:03:57,510 --> 00:03:58,658
You are a customer.

65
00:04:01,467 --> 00:04:04,074
Welcome back, Fumiko.

66
00:04:04,186 --> 00:04:05,154
She's late.

67
00:04:06,626 --> 00:04:07,648
I'm home.

68
00:04:07,673 --> 00:04:08,482
What were you doing

69
00:04:08,558 --> 00:04:09,713
You're fined

70
00:04:10,500 --> 00:04:11,439
I’m sorry.

71
00:04:30,574 --> 00:04:33,714
Happy birthday to you

72
00:04:34,257 --> 00:04:37,757
Happy birthday to you

73
00:04:37,879 --> 00:04:45,665
Happy birthday to you

74
00:04:47,431 --> 00:04:49,180
Blow out the candles.

75
00:04:49,180 --> 00:04:50,373
One breath.

76
00:05:01,610 --> 00:05:03,296
Dad? Are you alright?

77
00:05:03,523 --> 00:05:04,297
I'm alright.

78
00:05:04,793 --> 00:05:07,675
Turn it on.

79
00:05:07,802 --> 00:05:09,175
let's have a toast.

80
00:05:12,956 --> 00:05:16,470
Thank you for all your hard work, Dad

81
00:05:16,537 --> 00:05:17,384
Thanks.

82
00:05:20,647 --> 00:05:22,066
This is delicious.

83
00:05:22,509 --> 00:05:24,323
Let's eat

84
00:05:25,439 --> 00:05:29,275
It's ironic that the day of my retirement is my birthday.

85
00:05:31,750 --> 00:05:34,270
But they all became good girls

86
00:05:35,386 --> 00:05:39,640
Seven years ago I was at a loss as to what to do when your mother died,

87
00:05:47,210 --> 00:05:49,794
But they all grew really well

88
00:05:50,955 --> 00:05:54,379
I have retired, but luckily my next job has been decided

89
00:05:54,720 --> 00:05:56,858
I'll work at a real estate company.

90
00:05:57,255 --> 00:06:00,936
He says the monthly salary is 30,000 yen, so it's not bad.

91
00:06:01,055 --> 00:06:02,915
That's fine

92
00:06:03,335 --> 00:06:06,285
By the way, I received 1.5 million yen after tax as a severance pay.

93
00:06:06,310 --> 00:06:08,183
Oh, 1.5 million yen!

94
00:06:08,255 --> 00:06:11,159
Of this,I have 1 million yen in deposits, for a total of 2.5 million yen

95
00:06:12,729 --> 00:06:13,442
Oh yeah.

96
00:06:19,258 --> 00:06:20,024
Yes, this is it

97
00:06:27,211 --> 00:06:28,768
Hey everyone, come here.

98
00:06:36,051 --> 00:06:37,726
Wow, there aren't many 1 million yen.

99
00:06:37,751 --> 00:06:40,380
What are you talking about? It's 98 times your salary

100
00:06:40,380 --> 00:06:41,609
You do a lot of calculations.

101
00:06:41,634 --> 00:06:42,411
I work at accounting department.

102
00:06:42,562 --> 00:06:45,065
You're probably about 90 times

103
00:06:45,090 --> 00:06:47,443
The problem is how to use the 2.5 million yen

104
00:06:47,657 --> 00:06:52,002
The easiest thing to do is to deposit it in a bank or put it in a loan trust

105
00:06:52,800 --> 00:06:54,674
I think that's a good idea, but I have another idea

106
00:06:55,413 --> 00:06:59,620
The 2.5 million yen will be divided equally among the five people, including me.

107
00:07:00,337 --> 00:07:01,037
with 500,000 yen each.

108
00:07:01,570 --> 00:07:02,896
I agree.

109
00:07:02,921 --> 00:07:03,537
I'm against it.

110
00:07:03,834 --> 00:07:04,942
Oh, why

111
00:07:05,900 --> 00:07:07,632
This the money our dad got.

112
00:07:08,032 --> 00:07:10,703
What belongs to the father belongs to the daughter, right?

113
00:07:11,174 --> 00:07:12,141
I don't think so.

114
00:07:13,849 --> 00:07:14,889
What do you think, sister?

115
00:07:15,766 --> 00:07:16,743
…Well,

116
00:07:17,186 --> 00:07:18,627
wait a minute

117
00:07:18,850 --> 00:07:24,690
The reason I thought of this is that this 2.5 million
yen will end up being used to help everyone get married

118
00:07:24,767 --> 00:07:27,171
So I fear it will be unfair.

119
00:07:27,490 --> 00:07:31,070
If We spend too much on the first thing, We won't have enough for the next thing

120
00:07:31,095 --> 00:07:32,327
I hate the idea.

121
00:07:32,380 --> 00:07:33,470
Me either.

122
00:07:33,495 --> 00:07:35,635
I am the youngest so I will definitely have disadvantage.

123
00:07:35,660 --> 00:07:37,305
So we're all going to share it

124
00:07:37,840 --> 00:07:40,280
Kazuyo, give everyone 500,000 yen

125
00:07:40,280 --> 00:07:40,866
But...

126
00:07:40,890 --> 00:07:41,836
it's okay

127
00:07:43,995 --> 00:07:45,580
everyone is already grown up

128
00:07:45,830 --> 00:07:48,252
You can take responsibility for yourself, right?

129
00:07:50,153 --> 00:07:51,173
I'm not needed.

130
00:07:52,627 --> 00:07:55,120
Miyako, don't say that

131
00:07:55,120 --> 00:07:57,300
You're the only one in the house who don't work.

132
00:07:57,300 --> 00:08:00,150
You have to leave this house someday and get married

133
00:08:00,150 --> 00:08:02,560
If you don't treat me equally, I will be in trouble

134
00:08:03,429 --> 00:08:05,522
OK I will take it.

135
00:08:08,021 --> 00:08:10,560
Well, how you use this money is up to you,

136
00:08:11,100 --> 00:08:15,343
but I want to make sure that I've just given you all your marriage money

137
00:08:16,400 --> 00:08:21,866
Therefore, I would like to be released from my
financial obligations as a father as of today

138
00:08:22,017 --> 00:08:23,717
Are you relieved of the pressure?

139
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:27,097
However, I'm happy to give advice on mental health.

140
00:08:27,122 --> 00:08:28,798
of course, you are our father after all.

141
00:08:30,280 --> 00:08:31,290
Future living expenses...

142
00:08:31,290 --> 00:08:35,809
As before, you will have to pay 20% of your monthly salary. I will pay 10,000 yen

143
00:08:35,920 --> 00:08:37,440
That should be ok.

144
00:08:37,440 --> 00:08:40,262
Your income has decreased, so it's okay if it's less

145
00:08:40,287 --> 00:08:40,524
Yes,

146
00:08:40,548 --> 00:08:43,462
I'll give it because I don't have to save money for everyone anymore

147
00:08:45,060 --> 00:08:48,456
By the way, one last thing.

148
00:08:54,823 --> 00:08:56,471
I also want a little freedom

149
00:08:56,589 --> 00:08:58,363
What's the hell?

150
00:09:17,934 --> 00:09:18,611
Are you gonna for walking?

151
00:09:21,285 --> 00:09:23,699
I woke up at 6:30 like usual.

152
00:09:30,447 --> 00:09:34,380
Well...Miwako, listen to the dream I had on the night I retired

153
00:09:35,335 --> 00:09:38,243
This is a dream from 30 years ago when I was a new employee

154
00:09:38,543 --> 00:09:43,641
I made a mistake with calculation and the boss really scold me.

155
00:09:44,110 --> 00:09:47,790
You couldn't forget it because you were bad about Math.

156
00:09:48,415 --> 00:09:52,175
Plus, the chief passed away 10 years ago

157
00:09:53,150 --> 00:09:56,602
Even though I thought I had forgotten, I couldn't forget

158
00:09:57,530 --> 00:09:58,319
Is that so?

159
00:10:04,072 --> 00:10:04,561
Welcome.

160
00:10:04,586 --> 00:10:05,586
Good morning

161
00:10:07,501 --> 00:10:08,511
Is your father there?

162
00:10:09,173 --> 00:10:09,973
Yes.

163
00:10:10,845 --> 00:10:13,595
Yoshie-san's aunt is here.

164
00:10:13,675 --> 00:10:15,348
Good morning.

165
00:10:16,714 --> 00:10:22,400
Well, it's pretty clean and the flowers are in good shape

166
00:10:22,400 --> 00:10:25,270
I'm sure Miyako-san, 'll make a great wife

167
00:10:25,270 --> 00:10:27,710
Oh, are you eating now? Excuse me

168
00:10:27,710 --> 00:10:29,909
From today , I am in
a comfortable position.

169
00:10:30,206 --> 00:10:32,253
That's right

170
00:10:32,660 --> 00:10:36,900
My husband is jealous of you.

171
00:10:36,900 --> 00:10:39,180
But now that time has come,

172
00:10:39,180 --> 00:10:41,830
it feels like my life's work is over

173
00:10:41,830 --> 00:10:43,246
and I miss my work.

174
00:10:45,778 --> 00:10:50,125
Retirement means basically a declaration that
from today on you are an old man.

175
00:10:50,150 --> 00:10:54,938
Don't say that, your new second life is just beginning

176
00:10:55,270 --> 00:10:59,100
Actually, yes, I'm talking about a matchmaking.

177
00:10:59,100 --> 00:11:00,830
As you know, I have four girls,

178
00:11:00,830 --> 00:11:03,010
but they are all single.

179
00:11:03,010 --> 00:11:04,320
If you have any good men..

180
00:11:04,320 --> 00:11:08,930
Please introduce us in a raw.

181
00:11:08,930 --> 00:11:12,379
You are all really lovely ladies.

182
00:11:12,984 --> 00:11:14,910
They are picky.

183
00:11:14,910 --> 00:11:16,820
I was raising a child on my own.

184
00:11:16,820 --> 00:11:19,208
it must have been difficult

185
00:11:20,603 --> 00:11:24,096
By the way, about the marriage proposal?

186
00:11:25,816 --> 00:11:29,352
There is a nice woman for you.

187
00:11:29,739 --> 00:11:31,993
For me?

188
00:11:37,914 --> 00:11:39,642
Is it okay to take this?

189
00:11:41,273 --> 00:11:41,993
I feel sorry.

190
00:11:42,144 --> 00:11:42,770
Never mind.

191
00:11:43,120 --> 00:11:45,032
It's natural for me to devote myself to you,

192
00:11:45,057 --> 00:11:47,360
 I really appreciate your feelings.

193
00:11:47,385 --> 00:11:48,614
so please use them

194
00:11:49,539 --> 00:11:55,709
Really? Sorry. I'm heading home now

195
00:11:56,510 --> 00:11:58,232
You can check out what's inside

196
00:11:58,264 --> 00:12:02,394
I don't need to look it up.
I'm sure there is 50000yen.

197
00:12:02,720 --> 00:12:05,221
But just to be safe

198
00:12:13,486 --> 00:12:14,546
500000yen.

199
00:12:17,296 --> 00:12:19,720
What on earth is this?

200
00:12:19,720 --> 00:12:25,531
I really want you to use it

201
00:12:25,556 --> 00:12:31,947
...Oh, I'm going to call my brother

202
00:12:31,972 --> 00:12:33,500
I have to make him happy

203
00:12:33,500 --> 00:12:34,677
Excuse me

204
00:12:48,359 --> 00:12:49,339
Are you alone?

205
00:12:49,363 --> 00:12:50,035
No.

206
00:12:50,257 --> 00:12:51,510
With a guy.

207
00:13:01,857 --> 00:13:02,586
Excuse me.

208
00:13:31,129 --> 00:13:32,552
Welcome.

209
00:13:33,435 --> 00:13:34,795
Oh you are here.

210
00:13:36,520 --> 00:13:37,940
Welcome.

211
00:13:39,311 --> 00:13:40,684
There's no table.

212
00:13:40,877 --> 00:13:42,283
Come on,please wait.

213
00:13:43,812 --> 00:13:45,685
Go there.

214
00:13:46,288 --> 00:13:47,981
Thanks.

215
00:13:56,084 --> 00:13:57,130
Excuse me

216
00:13:57,130 --> 00:13:59,482
I'll clean it up right away.

217
00:14:01,449 --> 00:14:02,915
You came after all.

218
00:14:03,679 --> 00:14:06,090
You retired yesterday, didn't you?

219
00:14:06,090 --> 00:14:08,325
I thought you wouldn't come again

220
00:14:08,790 --> 00:14:11,319
I was worry about you.

221
00:14:11,403 --> 00:14:12,550
I'm glad.

222
00:14:15,633 --> 00:14:18,893
Hey, do you want to eat somewhere with me tonight?

223
00:14:20,785 --> 00:14:22,535
I was thinking of eating here.

224
00:14:22,560 --> 00:14:24,935
It's boring here.

225
00:14:25,450 --> 00:14:26,883
Thanks

226
00:14:27,363 --> 00:14:28,563
Thanks

227
00:14:32,265 --> 00:14:35,390
Let's go somewhere together

228
00:14:35,435 --> 00:14:36,069
We+ll be alone?

229
00:14:36,162 --> 00:14:37,002
You hate it?

230
00:14:37,343 --> 00:14:39,416
I don't mind if we're alone,

231
00:14:40,261 --> 00:14:44,165
please just have one of my feelings

232
00:14:47,380 --> 00:14:51,010
I will tell the boss that my brother was sick,

233
00:14:51,010 --> 00:14:53,114
Let's decide the time to meet.

234
00:15:14,925 --> 00:15:15,740
Excuse me

235
00:15:16,631 --> 00:15:16,953
Yes

236
00:15:19,760 --> 00:15:22,240
your companion will be arriving shortly.

237
00:15:22,240 --> 00:15:24,160
but would you like to take a bath?

238
00:15:24,160 --> 00:15:25,473
Ok.. Yes.

239
00:15:25,498 --> 00:15:27,371
that's right. Let's take a bath

240
00:15:44,978 --> 00:15:46,399
The bath is here

241
00:15:47,493 --> 00:15:49,327
Then, here is the toilet

242
00:16:06,115 --> 00:16:07,189
Hi.

243
00:16:08,621 --> 00:16:09,812
Sorry I'm late.

244
00:16:12,463 --> 00:16:14,248
I want to join in too

245
00:16:15,351 --> 00:16:17,924
You can't.
I'm embarrassed.

246
00:16:18,492 --> 00:16:19,959
Don't be shy.

247
00:16:22,045 --> 00:16:22,805
I wanna have a bath.

248
00:16:22,830 --> 00:16:23,519
Hey, come on.

249
00:16:24,763 --> 00:16:25,868
give me a break.

250
00:16:27,189 --> 00:16:28,052
Why?

251
00:16:28,898 --> 00:16:32,988
I've never taken a bath with died my ex wife either.

252
00:16:33,650 --> 00:16:36,069
If I go in with a woman, it'll hurt my heart

253
00:16:37,120 --> 00:16:43,065
Oh really? Too bad. Well, it's fine if I just want to wash your back.

254
00:16:44,740 --> 00:16:47,580
Let me do it.
You're pure.

255
00:16:48,613 --> 00:16:49,694
I like you

256
00:16:49,719 --> 00:16:50,361
Thanks.

257
00:16:53,856 --> 00:16:55,563
You love me?

258
00:16:56,290 --> 00:16:57,298
Of course

259
00:16:58,195 --> 00:16:59,345
How much?

260
00:16:59,425 --> 00:17:00,052
A lot.

261
00:17:00,302 --> 00:17:02,718
Can you show me the evidence later?

262
00:17:02,743 --> 00:17:04,580
Okay, I'll show you

263
00:17:05,085 --> 00:17:07,646
Then, say I'm a man.

264
00:17:07,752 --> 00:17:09,238
I'm a man.

265
00:17:09,340 --> 00:17:12,006
That's great. I'm happy.

266
00:17:24,771 --> 00:17:25,637
Have a beer.

267
00:17:34,859 --> 00:17:37,602
what's wrong? Are you cold?

268
00:17:37,813 --> 00:17:38,667
No.

269
00:17:40,552 --> 00:17:41,665
Have a beer.

270
00:17:43,505 --> 00:17:44,795
Thank you too

271
00:17:44,947 --> 00:17:46,040
Please.

272
00:17:46,220 --> 00:17:47,730
Thank you for your hard work

273
00:17:51,900 --> 00:17:56,781
You know what?, when I get drunk,will you treat me?

274
00:17:57,155 --> 00:17:59,085
I will.

275
00:17:59,109 --> 00:18:01,702
I'm so happy.
Cheers.

